# TypeScript

- `strict: true` in `tsconfig.json` — do not weaken.
- No casual `any`; use explicit types at SDK/hardware boundaries.
- Exhaustive `switch` on domain event unions in `src/app/` and `src/even/`.
- Small modules; one responsibility per file.
- Prefer plain functions over premature abstraction.
- Handle errors at integration boundaries; surface messages to the debug UI.
- Match existing import style: `.ts` extensions in relative imports.
